h_n(t)=\begin{cases} f(t-α)&t\in[n,n+α)\\ f(t+α)&t\in[n-α,n)\\ -f(t-α)&t\in[-n,-n+α)\\ -f(t+α)&t\in[-n-α,-n)\\ 0&\text{ everywhere else} \end{cases}
